HEADWORD: Pigsney
<hw>Pigs"ney</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <ety>[Perh. a dim. of Dan.
<ets>pige</ets> a girl, or Sw. <ets>piga</ets>; or from E. <ets>pig's
eye</ets>.]</ety> <def>A word of endearment for a girl or woman.</def>
<mark>[Obs.]</mark> <altsp>[Written also <asp>pigsnie</asp>,
